## JSONSyntaxError

**Severity:** error | **Type:** JSON | **Status:** Deprecated

This check has been deprecated and superseded by [ValidJSON](/developer-guide/platformos-check/checks/valid-json), which provides the same JSON syntax validation with additional schema validation support.

If you have `JSONSyntaxError` in your `.platformos-check.yml` configuration, replace it with `ValidJSON`.

## Migration

Replace any references to `JSONSyntaxError` in your configuration:

```yaml
# Before
JSONSyntaxError:
  enabled: true

# After
ValidJSON:
  enabled: true
```

